Add LoongArch64 type aliases for the cgo bridge.

creack/pty defines _C_int / _C_uint per-architecture in ztypes_<arch>.go.
The upstream catalogue stops at arm64/ppc64/riscv/s390x; this patch
appends a loong64 variant that matches the kernel ABI (int32 / uint32).

--- /dev/null
+++ b/ztypes_loong64.go
@@ -0,0 +1,10 @@
+//go:build loong64
+// +build loong64
+
+package pty
+
+type (
+	_C_int  int32
+	_C_uint uint32
+)
+
